Package: medinfoR
Title: R Client for the medinfo Pharmaceutical Information API
Version: 1.0.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Dominik", "Selzer", , "dominik.selzer@uni-saarland.de",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Simeon", "Rüdesheim", , "simeon.ruedesheim@uni-saarland.de",
           role = c("aut", "ctb"))
    )
Description: Provides a complete R interface to the medinfo API
    (<https://github.com/Clinical-Pharmacy-Saarland-University/abdataapi-go>),
    a pharmaceutical information service developed at Clinical Pharmacy
    Saarland University. Covers drug-drug interaction checks (by PZN and
    compound name, single and batch), adverse drug reactions, pharmacogenetic
    guidelines (PharmGKB), PRISCUS classifications for elderly patients, QT
    prolongation risk, product information, formulation codes, and full user
    account management.
